- Deep learning has already transformed traditional internet businesses like web search and advertising, and is enabling brand new products and businesses to be created
- Course sequence on Coursera will help learners gain and master the skills of deep learning
- AI is the new electricity, and deep learning is driving a lot of developments
- Course 1: Learn foundations of neural networks, build a neural network, and train it on data to recognize cats
- Course 2: Learn practical aspects of deep learning, such as hyperparameter tuning, regularization, and advanced optimization algorithms
- Course 3: Learn how to structure a machine learning project, best practices for splitting data, and when to use end-to-end deep learning
- Course 4: Learn about convolutional neural networks and how to apply them to images
- Course 5: Learn about sequence models and how to apply them to natural language processing and other problems
